query:
SELECT t.ticket, t.symbol, t.type, t.status, t.profit, t.openTime
FROM trades t
JOIN trading_accounts ta ON t.accountId = ta.id
WHERE ta.accountNumber = '163032743'
ORDER BY t.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 5;
